TextElement.Str: Fuchsia for KLWP has been successfully installed! Make sure you have KLWP set as your home and lock screen wallpapers.
Make sure you have all four installed for best results. Also, for some system toggles to work, your phone will need to be rooted, and you will need to enable System+ in Secure Settings.
Keep in mind, Fuchsia requires the following apps to function as intended:
To finish installing Fuchsia, you'll need to import a couple tasks in Tasker. First we'll:
• Open Tasker • Hold down on the Home icon down the bottom left • Select Import • Select Fuchsia
And now you're ready to go!
If it pops up on your screen, please select Nova Launcher.
Please open Secure Settings, scroll to the System+ tab and hit enable to enable system toggles.
Are you sure you have KLWP Pro installed?
KLWP Pro is required to import this theme.
Are you sure you have Nova Launcher installed?
Nova Launcher is required to import this theme.
Some parts of this theme require root access. Do you currently currently have root access?
Are you sure you have Secure Settings installed?
Secure Settings is required to run some parts of this theme.
Are you sure you have Tasker installed?
Tasker is required to run parts of this theme.
